  "title": "Delivery Driver Cum Logistics Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Carry out deliveries of the full range of products as assigned by your immediate manager</li>\n  <li>Ensure workplace health, hygiene, and safety requirements are met</li>\n  <li>Ensure the safe receipt, storage, retrieval, timely packing, and dispatch of goods</li>\n  <li>Assist in other warehousing and/or logistics activities when necessary</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Welfare &amp; Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>13th Month Salary</li>\n  <li>Meal Allowance</li>\n  <li>Performance Bonus</li>\n  <li>Birthday Incentives</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefits</li>\n  <li>Staff Discount</li>\n  <li>Festive Gifting</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum GCE ‘N’ or ‘O’ Level qualification</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid Class 3 Singapore Driving License</li>\n  <li>Hardworking and willing to learn</li>\n  <li>Mature and responsible</li>\n  <li>Must be able to assist with other warehousing and/or logistics activities and must be able to lift cartons weighing up to 15kg</li>\n  <li>5.5 days work week</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>\n<p>Please include a detailed recent resume, indicating reasons for leaving, last drawn salary, expected salary and date of availability.</p>",
